    • Constructor Detail

      • UrlTrie

        public UrlTrie(String rootPage,
               Collection<String> pages)
        Parameters:
        rootPage - use the longest common prefix as your _root page. e.g. if your pages are "www.linkedin.com/in/", "www.linkedin.com/jobs/", "www.linkedin.com/groups/" The longest common prefix is "www.linkedin.com/", and it will be your _root page. And the last "/" will be used as a TrieRoot.
        pages -

      • UrlTrie
